Package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.util.stream

Interface PrimitiveOutputStream

All Known Implementing Classes:
ByteBufferStream
public interface PrimitiveOutputStream
An output stream that allows accessors to write primitive types to it. It supports all primitives that are required to process Corfu messages and payloads.
